== Reaction Formula ==
* With identifiers:
** 1 [[MET]][c] '''+''' 1 [[ATP]][c] '''+''' 1 [[WATER]][c] '''=>''' 1 [[Pi]][c] '''+''' 1 [[S-ADENOSYLMETHIONINE]][c] '''+''' 1 [[PPI]][c]
* With common name(s):
** 1 L-methionine[c] '''+''' 1 ATP[c] '''+''' 1 H2O[c] '''=>''' 1 phosphate[c] '''+''' 1 S-adenosyl-L-methionine[c] '''+''' 1 diphosphate[c]

